sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Користувач
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant ApiService
    participant Local as SharedPreferences
    participant API as FastAPI comments
    participant Files as uploads/
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant TG as Telegram Bot API
    participant FCM as Firebase Cloud Messaging

    User->>App: Додає коментар
    App->>ApiService: addComment(taskId, text, files)
    alt мережа доступна
        ApiService->>API: POST /tasks/{task_id}/comments multipart/form-data
        API->>DB: insert TaskMessage
        loop файли
            API->>Files: write upload
            API->>DB: insert MessageMedia
        end
        API->>DB: commit
        API->>DB: load task assignments and admins
        loop отримувачі
            API->>TG: send comment notification
            API->>FCM: send comment push
        end
        API-->>ApiService: TaskMessageResponse
        ApiService->>ApiService: syncOfflineQueue()
    else network error
        ApiService->>Local: append offline_action_queue add_comment
        ApiService-->>App: queued locally
    end

    Note over ApiService,Local: Наступний успішний запит або refresh task list
    ApiService->>Local: read offline_action_queue
    loop queued actions
        ApiService->>API: replay add_comment / complete_task
    end
    ApiService->>Local: remove successful actions
